reviewText: My wife and I are big "Flashpoint" fans, and having these to watch is terrific. "Flashpoint" features great ensemble acting, the story lines are tight and believable, and there's no embarrassing sex scenes and stuff like that, which I've always disliked watching. Awesome show and Christian-safe. NOTE: We ordered season 5 quite a few weeks ago and are planning to investigate. Could be they're not available yet.
